10:44.386 --> 10:47.587
<i>[SMOOTH SMALTZY POP MUSIC]</i>

10:47.588 --> 10:48.689
<i>♪</i>

10:48.690 --> 10:50.091
- Whoa.
- Look at this.

10:50.092 --> 10:52.960
