10:52.961 --> 10:54.070
Hey, guys.

10:54.358 --> 10:55.916
What the hell are you guys doing here?

10:55.941 --> 10:58.042
We're here to support you on your big day.

10:58.067 --> 10:59.922
- I took the day off of work.
- We all did.

10:59.922 --> 11:01.043
Well, not you, Tommy.

11:01.043 --> 11:02.367
Technically, this is still work for you.

11:02.367 --> 11:03.869
- In fact, get me a coffee, man.
- Right away.

11:03.870 --> 11:05.966
- Would you look at those!
- Oh.

11:05.991 --> 11:08.024
Sit in your chairs so I can
take pictures of you in 'em.

11:08.025 --> 11:09.994
Come on, Chrissy, that's embarrassing.

11:09.995 --> 11:12.162
This is work for us, it's not like fun.

11:13.333 --> 11:14.999
[SOFT SQUEAL] Got it.

11:15.000 --> 11:17.568
[SQUEALING] Oh, look at you, so cute!

11:17.569 --> 11:19.011
Actually, it's sexy, so.

11:19.570 --> 11:22.906
- And action.
- We at Little Caesars

11:22.907 --> 11:25.749
want to find out what
it would take to stop you

11:25.910 --> 11:27.477
from enjoying our pizza.

11:27.478 --> 11:30.094
Introducing test item 423...

11:30.882 --> 11:32.782
- a football.
- Cut!

11:33.465 --> 11:34.818
That's excellent, Brian.

11:34.819 --> 11:36.559
Excellent? It wasn't very funny.

11:36.622 --> 11:38.021
That wasn't funny at all.

11:38.022 --> 11:40.792
I mean, should it be like...
Should he make a funnier face?

11:40.793 --> 11:42.309
