11:42.521 --> 11:44.179
Like, could he say "frickin' football"?

11:44.179 --> 11:46.581
[LAUGHS] That's funny.

11:46.581 --> 11:48.236
- [CHUCKLES]
- Go tell him.

11:48.874 --> 11:51.384
Oh, no, I can't...
They're doing their thing.

11:51.385 --> 11:52.919
Yeah, we're not directing this one.

11:52.920 --> 11:54.136
It's your commercial.

11:54.523 --> 11:57.090
I'm sure they'd be
interested in your ideas.

11:57.091 --> 11:58.760
You guys make everything better.

12:00.963 --> 12:02.610
We can probably... fly in one note.

12:02.641 --> 12:04.341
- We can fly in one note.
- And roll it up!

12:04.342 --> 12:05.838
- One note.
- I think so.

12:06.655 --> 12:07.786
Rolling!

12:11.382 --> 12:13.184
And action.

12:13.185 --> 12:15.173
We had a quick note. Something to add.

12:15.453 --> 12:17.212
Cut. Who the fuck are you?

12:17.924 --> 12:20.457
Tim Cramblin. Cramblin Duvet Advertising.

12:20.458 --> 12:22.638
We... we actually met before your bath.

12:22.638 --> 12:24.005
What the fuck are you doing here?

12:24.006 --> 12:25.373
Uh... oh, we actually

12:25.374 --> 12:27.041
came up with the idea for this commercial.

12:27.042 --> 12:29.277
Yeah, we have a couple of, uh,
chairs with our names on them.

12:29.278 --> 12:30.806
I don't give a shit. Reilly.

12:31.314 --> 12:32.582
I have a limited amount of time here.

12:32.583 --> 12:33.882
